doctype html
html(lang='en')
	head
	meta(http-equiv='Content-Type',content='text/html; charset=utf-8')
	meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no")
	meta(name="keywords" content="")
	meta(name="description" content="")
	title Welcome to Our wedding
	link(rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png" href="images/favicon.png")
	link(rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/bundle.css")
	link(rel="stylesheet" href="src/css/index.css")
	body
	div.loading-overlay
		img(src="images/loading.svg")
		audio(src="http://o7q84v6xt.bkt.clouddn.com/beautiful_tmp.mp3" type="audio/mpeg" loop autoplay)
	div(class='swiper-container')
		div(class='swiper-wrapper')
			div(class='swiper-slide slide-1')
				div(class="item-image animated" data-ani-name="bounceIn" data-ani-duration="5s" data-ani-delay="0s")
				p(class="item-text animated" data-ani-name="rollIn" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="0.2s") We Are 范雄 & 何谐
				p(class="item-text1 animated" data-ani-name="rollIn" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="1.2s") Going to Marry
				p(class="item-text2 animated" data-ani-name="rollIn" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="2.2s") In 绵阳 on 2016.6.25
				p(class="item-text3 animated" data-ani-name="shake" data-ani-duration="6s" data-ani-delay="3.2s") Welcome to Our's Wedding!
			div(class='swiper-slide slide-2')
				div(class="item-image animated" data-ani-name="slideInLeft" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="0s")
				p(class="item-text2 animated" data-ani-name="rollIn" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="0.2s") Our Story can be traced back
				p(class="item-text1 animated" data-ani-name="rollIn" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="1.2s") to 14 years when we first knew each other
			div(class='swiper-slide slide-5')
				div(class="item-image animated" data-ani-name="slideInLeft" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="0s")
				p(class="item-text animated" data-ani-name="rollIn" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="0.2s") Another 10 years after graduation,We met again
				//p(class="item-text1 animated" data-ani-name="rollIn" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="1.2s") We go dating seeing movie,eating and watching shows.
			div(class='swiper-slide slide-6')
				div(class="item-image animated" data-ani-name="slideInLeft" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="0s") 
				p(class="item-text animated" data-ani-name="rollIn" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="0.2s") We are both loving delicious food,plesant trip and old classic moives.
			div(class='swiper-slide slide-7')
				div(class="item-image animated" data-ani-name="slideInLeft" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="0s")
				p(class="item-text2 animated" data-ani-name="rollIn" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="0.2s") The encounter of Fireworks Festival
				p(class="item-text3 animated" data-ani-name="rollIn" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="1.2s") We make our wishes with fireworks blooming in the sky
			div(class='swiper-slide slide-8')
				div(class="item-image animated" data-ani-name="slideInLeft" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="0s")
				p(class="item-text animated" data-ani-name="rollIn" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="0.2s") I proposed to her under the sea in Redang Island
				p(class="item-text1 animated" data-ani-name="rollIn" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="1.2s") And We decide to pursue of our happiness and dreams together in the rest of our life.
			div(class='swiper-slide slide-9')
				div(class="item-image animated" data-ani-name="slideInLeft" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="0s")
				p(class="item-text animated" data-ani-name="rollIn" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="0.2s") Now,We are going to have our marriage ceremony be held
				p(class="item-text1 animated" data-ani-name="rollIn" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="1.2s") And U r all welcomed!
			div(class='swiper-slide slide-4')
				div(class="item-image animated" data-ani-name="slideInLeft" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="0s")
				div(class="item-image-loc animated" data-ani-name="slideInLeft" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="0s")
						p(class="location") 地址:四川绵阳绵州印象
						input(id="getLocation" type="image" src="images/nav.svg") 
						//button#getLocation 路线
				p(class="item-text animated" data-ani-name="wobble" data-ani-duration="1s" data-ani-delay="0.3s") ----We Will Be Here Waiting For U----
			div(class='swiper-slide slide-3')
				p(class="item-text animated" data-ani-name="shake" data-ani-duration="10s" data-ani-delay="0s") Write Something for Us
				div(id="commentWrap" class="comment-warp")

	button.up-arrow
		i.icon-angle-double-up
	button.btn-music
		i.icon-note
